{"type": "article", "id": 49547, "title": "耐克推出PS4主题球鞋，Anna Sui为麦当劳设计狗年红包 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-01-24T04:21:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 47266, "name": "狗年"}, {"id": 738, "name": "麦当劳"}, {"id": 1036, "name": "耐克"}, {"id": 1297, "name": "阿迪达斯"}, {"id": 47286, "name": "亚瑟士"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180124120159Jos4xeYSDiqbF2NX.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">又是跨界</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://lanxiongsports.com/?c=posts&amp;a=view&amp;id=9125\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>耐克公司和索尼合作推出以 PlayStation 为主题的球鞋</b></a> Nike PG-2 PlayStation Colorway，并以保罗·乔治的第二代签名鞋的形式上市。这双联名版本采用 PS4 游戏机联名配色，搭载了许多独有元素，包含会发光的鞋舌、PlayStation Logo、游戏手把操控按钮的图样等。2 月 10 日正式发售，价格为 110 美元。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801241140092l7gSohtQ1HsjYkR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.621538\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://socialbeta.com/t/jiafangyifang-news-20180123\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>麦当劳与华裔时装设计师 Anna Sui 合作</b></a>，为庆祝中国农历新年在美国限量发行「狗年幸运红包」。这些限量版红包印有哈巴狗、柴犬等亚洲犬种图案，将于 1 月 23 日在旧金山举办线下活动抽奖获得。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124115444w8rmafKv5UcBYV13.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NDAwMDk4MA==&amp;mid=2668034937&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=504d9853ccb80aec70792cbbdcd9cb03&amp;chksm=bc7c22428b0bab54c3a80a5c3c544efcf736c0d4f95e2febcb6ce22a7fd2e1830d12c5ede6ec&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0124R911DOLg6a3nQAoKKp0g&amp;key=df844c06b1ea86337ae77f4169233d76c683f2dd806afeb388837142cba3227564041be50ffef9bba2051076e4e05a33a84446ae050989af35e13fb741d83157c73ab658e568945f5b9f6d1879d984ef&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.10.5+build(14F2511)&amp;version=11000006&amp;lang=zh_CN&amp;pass_ticket=odIR8TBgnpEZzLpilDlh2Pc2igEdkufjo3AuMT7UdSOXyOJKm0TEwTckXXEttQdl\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>麦当劳 X 《捉妖记2》推出春节新品</b></a>，并发布一支新品广告，几款新品看起来还蛮诱人的……</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=d0537o3ke4d&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p><a href=\"http://lanxiongsports.com/?c=posts&amp;a=view&amp;id=9126\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>亚瑟士首次签约中国代言人</b></a>，江疏影、李治廷成为亚瑟士（ASICS）2018 年大中华区品牌代言人。半个月前，李宇春刚刚代替井柏然成为亚瑟士旗下的子品牌鬼塚虎新一任大中华区代言人。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113252Xa3dw7xhlpveN9so.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p class=\"\"><b>adidas Originals<a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/25437.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">&nbsp;发布 2018 年度大片《Keep Pushin'》</a>，</b>鹿晗、Nick YOUNG&nbsp;等多位明星出镜。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=c0536ybhn89&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/25474.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">林更新出演乐事新年微电影《追》</a>，</b>预告片 1 分 12 秒，目前腾讯视频上的播放量超过 149 万次，正片将于本月 25 日发布。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=w0025iu9nvd&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/diesels-new-ad-celebrating-flaws-has-great-storytelling-that-flies-off-in-all-directions/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Diesel 继续去年 Go with the Flaw 后又推出系列广告</b></a>。这次拍了一个招风耳男和大鼻子女各自整容后相识相爱的故事，就当你以为这个广告居然如此“政治不正确”的时候，没想到他俩生下的孩子兼具爸妈的缺点，孩子骑在爸爸头上，最后文案是：Flaws always win。</p><p class=\"\"></p><figure><img src=\"img/uploads/20180124115329Dcu0iEYfNKOvy89q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></figure><p><a href=\"http://cny2018cp.nestlechinese.com/pages/?mz_ca=2069227&amp;mz_sp=7CPhb\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>雀巢中国新年营销</b></a>，在 H5 中内嵌了一支贺岁广告片，还可以上传照片体验各个时代的全家福。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124115551r8nOmS5zE2F9hZkD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来源：麦当劳<br></p><style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939; min-height: 19.0px} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 29.0px 'Hiragino Sans GB'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 29.0px 'Hiragino Sans GB'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 44.0px} span.s1 {font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-kerning: none; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #393939} span.s2 {font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 29.0px 'Hiragino Sans GB'; font-kerning: none} </style>"}